Due to the no-fly zone, many [Yemenis have been stranded in countries across
the world](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2015/03/31/yemens-no-fly-zone-
thousands-of-yemenis-are-stranded-abroad/), which prompted Yemeni netizens
such as Khaled al-Hammadi to launch the hashtag
[#Stranded_Yemenis](https://twitter.com/search?q=stranded_Yemenis&src=typd).

> 1000s of
> [#Stranded_Yemenis](https://twitter.com/hashtag/Stranded_Yemenis?src=hash)
